chart.description: Number of backends currently connected to this database. This is the only column in this view that returns a value reflecting current state; all other columns return the accumulated values since the last reset. (gauge)
chart.name: Connected Backends

chart.description: Number of rows fetched, inserted, updated and deleted by queries in this database
chart.name: # Rows
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_stat_database_tup_fetched', rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('pg_stat_database_tup_inserted', rollup='latest').publish(label='B')
C = data('pg_stat_database_tup_updated', rollup='latest').publish(label='C')
D = data('pg_stat_database_tup_deleted', rollup='latest').publish(label='D')
E = data('pg_stat_database_tup_returned', rollup='latest').publish(label='E')

chart.description: Number of committed/rolled back transactions in this database
chart.name: Transactions
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_stat_database_xact_commit', rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('pg_stat_database_xact_rollback', rollup='latest').publish(label='B')

chart.name: Swap used/total
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.nodes.system.swap_total', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).sum(by=['node']).publish(label='A')
B = data('gauge.nodes.system.swap_used', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).sum(by=['node']).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Total Operations Per Second
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.nodes.ops', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).mean(by=['node']).publish(label='A')
B = data('gauge.nodes.cmd_get', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).mean(by=['node']).publish(label='B', enable=False)

chart.name: Rows Affected/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_stat_database_tup_inserted', rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('pg_stat_database_tup_updated', rollup='latest').publish(label='B')
C = data('pg_stat_database_tup_deleted', rollup='latest').publish(label='C')

chart.name: Memory headroom
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.bucket.op.mem_used', filter=filter('bucket', 'custom_bucket')).sum(by=['bucket']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('gauge.bucket.op.ep_mem_high_wat', filter=filter('bucket', 'custom_bucket')).sum(by=['bucket']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B-A).publish(label='C')

chart.description: Number of connections in this state
chart.name: PostgreSQL Connections
Disk fetches (misses)
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.nodes.ep_bg_fetched', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).mean(by=['node']).publish(label='A')
B = data('gauge.nodes.cmd_get', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).mean(by=['node']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A / B * 100).publish(label='C')
D = data('gauge.nodes.ep_bg_fetched', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).publish(label='D', enable=False)

chart.name: Highest disk used by couchbase per node
Disk space used by Couchbase
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.nodes.couch_docs_actual_disk_size', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).mean(by=['node']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('gauge.nodes.couch_docs_data_size', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).mean(by=['node']).publish(label='B')
C = (A - B).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Database Size
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_total_relation_size_bytes', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = (A).timeshift('1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = ((A-B)/B*100).publish(label='D')
E = ((A-C)/C*100).publish(label='E')

chart.name: Memory used per node
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.nodes.system.mem_free').mean(by=['node']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('gauge.nodes.system.mem_total').mean(by=['node']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B * 100).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C).min().publish(label='D')
E = (C).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='E')
F = (C).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='F')
G = (C).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='G')
H = (C).max().publish(label='H')

chart.name: CPU utilization per node
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.nodes.system.cpu_utilization_rate').mean(by=['node']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).max().publish(label='B')
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Gets and cache hits
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.nodes.cmd_get', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).mean(by=['node']).publish(label='A')
B = data('gauge.nodes.ep_bg_fetched').mean(by=['node']).publish(label='B')
C = ((A - B)/A * 100).publish(label='C')
D = (A - B).publish(label='D')

chart.name: Out of memory errors
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.bucket.op.ep_tmp_oom_errors', filter=filter('bucket', 'custom_bucket')).sum(by=['bucket']).publish(label='A')
B = data('gauge.bucket.op.ep_oom_errors', filter=filter('bucket', 'custom_bucket')).sum(by=['bucket']).publish(label='B')

chart.description: Number of queries in this database that have been canceled due to deadlocks
chart.name: Queries Cancelled (Deadlocks)
Out of memory errors per bucket
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.bucket.op.ep_oom_errors').sum(by=['bucket']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('gauge.bucket.op.ep_tmp_oom_errors').sum(by=['bucket']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A + B).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Highest memory used per node (%)
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.nodes.system.mem_free').mean(by=['node']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('gauge.nodes.system.mem_total').mean(by=['node']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = data('gauge.nodes.system.mem_free').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = ((1 - A/B) * 100).publish(label='D')

chart.name: Memory Free / Used
chart.programText:

B = data('gauge.nodes.mem_used', filter=filter('node', '10.1.68.194:8091')).mean(by=['node']).publish(label='B')

chart.description: Time spent writing/reading data file blocks by backends in this database, in milliseconds
